  def test_log_merge
    c1 = '420eac97a826bfac8724b6b0eef35c20922124b7'
    c2 = '30e367cef2203eba2b341dc9050993b06fd1e108'
    out = @git.rev_list({:pretty => 'raw', :max_count => 10}, 'master')
    assert_match "commit #{c1}", out
    assert_match "commit #{c2}", out
  end
